I"G<h1 id="calendar-widget">Calendar Widget</h1>

<p>Calendar widget for Awesome WM - slightly improved version of the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">wibox.widget.calendar</code>.</p>

<h2 id="features">Features</h2>

<h3 id="customization">Customization</h3>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Name</th>
      <th>Default</th>
      <th>Description</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>theme</td>
      <td><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">naughty</code></td>
      <td>The theme to use</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>placement</td>
      <td><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">top</code></td>
      <td>The position of the popup</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>radius</td>
      <td>8</td>
      <td>The popup radius</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>start_sunday</td>
      <td>false</td>
      <td>Start the week on Sunday</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>themes:</p>

    <table>
      <thead>
